    rotation using the
<span class="media"><span class="media media-image"><img src="figures/rotation-locked-symbolic.svg" class="media media-inline" alt="rotation lock"></span></span> button at the bottom of the <span class="gui"><a href="shell-introduction.html.ja#systemmenu" title="System menu">system menu</a></span>. To unlock, press the 
